 Cover Co., Ltd.宣布首个海外基地“COVER USA”，以发展粉丝社区并扩大销售网络https://www.moguravr.com/cover-usa/ノンジャンル人生 Tue, 12 Mar 2024 04:47:06 +0000 VTuberホロライブカバーUSA https://www.moguravr.com/?p=247745 <p>运营VTuber团体Hololive的Cover Co., Ltd.宣布设立首个海外据点COVER USA。 （摘自新闻发布会，Cover Co., Ltd.代表谷乡元明）根据Cover Co., Ltd.的公告，全球IP业务市场[…]</p><p>邮报<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/cover-usa/">Cover株式会社宣布首个海外据点“COVER USA”首先在</a><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上亮相，以发展粉丝社区并扩大销售网络。</p> ; <p>运营VTuber团体<a href="https://hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hololive</a>的<a href="https://cover-corp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cover Co., Ltd.</a>宣布设立首个海外据点<strong>COVER USA</strong> 。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.j7edya1j3w08-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.j7edya1j3w08-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.j7edya1j3w08-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.j7edya1j3w08-300x225.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.j7edya1j3w08-768x576.webp 768w" width="1000" height="750" /></a><br /> （摘自新闻发布会、Cover Co., Ltd.代表谷乡元明）</p><p>根据Cover Inc.的公告，日本和美国在全球IP业务市场中处于领先地位，总收入排名前十的角色大部分都是动漫造型。他解释说，为了未来在全球范围内开发知识产权，需要在英语国家拥有一个可以通过授权、内容销售和合作项目创收的商业环境。</p><p>在此背景下，Cover Inc. 在北美开设了“COVER USA”。这将是加速全球业务和内容发展的第一步，旨在将“VTuber”文化提升为继漫画、动画和游戏之后能够在世界范围内竞​​争的日本新内容产业。</p><p>通过在北美建立基地，公司旨在实现内容本地化、UGC本地化、业务本地化。该公司表示将加深与当地社区的关系，发展粉丝社区并扩大销售网络。</p><p>运营计划于 2024 年 7 月后开始。该公司将位于加利福尼亚州，并由 Tanigo 先生代表。</p><p>当被问及“有没有在海外建立3D现场表演工作室的愿景？”时，回答是“我们会考虑人才的需求后考虑，但Cover的首要任务（包括人才）是产品。目的是扩大业务并加强销售。”</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.g7n1yi4njkcg-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.g7n1yi4njkcg-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.g7n1yi4njkcg-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.g7n1yi4njkcg-300x155.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.g7n1yi4njkcg-768x398.webp 768w" width="1000" height="518" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.igyehdfh2bm8-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.igyehdfh2bm8-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.igyehdfh2bm8-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.igyehdfh2bm8-300x155.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.igyehdfh2bm8-768x396.webp 768w" width="1000" height="515" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.g2lyxruer5ft-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.g2lyxruer5ft-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.g2lyxruer5ft-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.g2lyxruer5ft-300x155.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/ef2aed59ddf5bb508b5b6a4f1db9d27b-kix.g2lyxr